g.text: A fundamental architectural decision is where to run your model's predictions (inference). The choice between the user's device and

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: your server has massive implications for cost, speed, and privacy.

g.text: - ✅ **Powerful Compute:** Can run massive, complex models that wouldn't fit on a phone.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **Easy to Update:** Update the model on your server once, and all users get it instantly.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **Secure Model IP:** Your proprietary model never leaves your control.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **High Cost:** You pay for every second the server is running.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **High Latency:** Predictions are slow due to network round-trip time.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Requires Connectivity:** Useless without an internet connection.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Privacy Concerns:** User data must be sent to your servers.

g.text: - ✅ **Low Cost:** The user provides the compute. Your server costs are minimal.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **Low Latency:** Inference is nearly instant, with no network lag.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **Works Offline:** The model can run anywhere, anytime.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **High Privacy:** User data never leaves the device.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Limited Compute:** Models must be small and highly optimized.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Hard to Update:** You have to push a new app update to every user.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Model is Exposed:** Your model can be reverse-engineered.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Batch Prediction (Asynchronous): We pre-calculate predictions for many or all users on a schedule (e.g., every 24 hours). When a user

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: needs a prediction, we simply look it up from a database.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Online Prediction (Synchronous): We wait for a user to make a request. The system then generates the prediction in real-time and returns

g.text: - ✅ **Hides Model Latency:** The user gets an instant response because the prediction is just a fast database lookup.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **High Throughput:** Can efficiently compute millions of predictions offline using massive parallel jobs (e.g., Spark).

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Stale Predictions:** The user's prediction is only as fresh as the last batch job.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Wasted Compute:** Often calculates predictions for users who may not log in, wasting resources.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ✅ **Efficient Compute:** Only computes predictions when they are actually requested.

g.text: - ❌ **Latency Sensitive:** The user has to wait for the model to run. The model must be fast.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: - ❌ **Lower Throughput:** Harder to batch inputs, making it less computationally efficient than large offline jobs.

g.text: Large, state-of-the-art models are powerful but often too slow and memory-intensive for production. A 1-second

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: prediction latency is unacceptable for most real-time applications.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: The Goal: To reduce the model's size (memory footprint) and latency (prediction speed) without significantly

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Identifies and removes redundant or unimportant model parameters (weights). This makes the network

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: "sparse," reducing its size and often speeding up computation.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: Reduces the numerical precision of the model's weights. Storing weights as 8-bit integers instead of 32-bit floating-

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: point numbers can lead to a 4x reduction in model size.

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji
Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: A large, accurate "teacher" model is used to train a smaller, faster "student" model. The student learns to replicate the

text.font-family: Excalifont, Xiaolai, sans-serif, Segoe UI Emoji

g.text: teacher's output, capturing its complex patterns in a more compact form.
